00:21:04.720 --> 00:21:05.860
Senhor, está bem?

00:21:15.510 --> 00:21:16.220
Coelho.

00:21:20.790 --> 00:21:21.180
Sim.

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:26.220
Miss Bai,

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.050
