00:24:38.510 --> 00:24:39.420
Changhe enviou-o?

00:24:41.200 --> 00:24:42.460
Sim, fez.

00:24:43.240 --> 00:24:44.530
Ele disse-me para te parar,

00:24:44.790 --> 00:24:45.490
