00:32:52.350 --> 00:32:53.940
das toxinas

00:32:53.960 --> 00:32:54.940
utilizando esta técnica.

00:32:55.640 --> 00:32:56.860
Quanto aos pensamentos

00:32:56.920 --> 00:32:58.290
tem,

00:32:59.070 --> 00:33:00.180
